  (alu load-status-r nop r0 gr::*save-status* bw-32)
  (alu setl nop gr::*save-trap-pc*  gr::*save-right*  bw-32)
  (alu setl nop gr::*save-trap-pc+* gr::*save-right*  bw-32)
  (move nop gr::*save-oreg* bw-32 next-pc-dispatch br-jindir)
